              },
              "displayName": "Arun Murthy",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
            },
            "body": "Apart from the default FIFO scheduler, none of the existing schedulers in hadoop-1.x support application priority - this leads to very interesting corner cases, resource deadlocks etc. which no one yet supports.\n\nWith YARN it's much more feasible, but not yet implemented.\n\nHope that helps...",
            "updateAuthor": {
              "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=acmurthy",
              "name": "acmurthy",
              "key": "acmurthy",
              "avatarUrls": {
