              "displayName": "Nemon Lou",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Asia/Shanghai"
            },
            "body": "Finally i use two Queues in Capacity Scheduler to basically meet our needs.\nBoth queue has a Absolute Max Capacity of 100% .The queue with higher priority has more Absolute Capacity configured(85%).\nJob which need high priority will be submitted to the queue which has more Absolute Capacity configured.",
